											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[LILI] Adventurer walks up to Moonrise with a map, headache, and in next cut he's strapped ot a chair, and a mindflayer approaches and puts a tadpole in his eye" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="Attitude" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Default" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="A boot stomps on a jutting piece of land (like the final step to get to the top of Everest.) The other boot follows. The adventurer has stopped there. A map in his hand. He's arrived: Moonrise Towers (before the shadow-curse.)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Cut to: mind flayer approaching the back of a board on which the adventurer is strapped and struggling. The mind flayer carries a tadpole (throwback to intro cinematic.) Closeup of the adventurer's eye as the tadpole goes in. Fade to black to screams of the adventurer. Fade in: Shot of the same room, clasps being undone on the board. A naked mind flayer rises - the Emperor. " />
										</node>
